{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2155320/extras/Banner-Welcome.png?t=1736177795\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Athos BlackThorne is the lord of the castle\u00a0but this may be his last day. Caught between the accusations of the Church, the claims of the Empire and the resistance of the indigenous peoples of the BlackForest, he will fall into a web of conspiracy, treason and deceit that seeks to replace him as the ruling power in the region. His last resort is turning to a cursed artifact that saved his family several times in the past - but at what cost? With this power in hand, Athos must face a series of tragical events, navigating his choices, allies and foes to figure out how to survive what may be the last dawn of the BlackThorne Keep. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>ENGAGING DELIBERATE DIRECTIONAL COMBAT</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2155320/extras/AthosCombat01-ezgif.com-optimize.gif?t=1736177795\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><i>Combat is paced, deliberate and mortally strategical - Your Mastery will be tested!</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>EXPLORE A BRAND NEW MEDIEVAL WORLD</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2155320/extras/AthosExplore01-ezgif.com-optimize.gif?t=1736177795\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><i>Dozens of locations and secrets to discover and explore</i></strong><br>The World of Paragonia is based on a low fantasy tabletop RPG that takes place in a world that imagines how a medieval colonial era would be.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>SOLVE INSTIGATING PUZZLES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2155320/extras/Investiage_Gif.gif?t=1736177795\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i><strong>Solve mysteries within\u00a0 Ancient Ruins and Sherathian cities.</strong></i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>BUILT WITH PASSION</strong><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2155320/extras/BuiltWithPassion-ezgif.com-optimize.gif?t=1736177795\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Started by a single Developer, 20 years in the making.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Based on the BlackThorne Keep tabletop RPG and on the exploits of the BlackThorne Keep gaming community, this is the culmination of 20 years of gaming across multiple medias. A homage to two decades of gathered stories and friends. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2155320/extras/DivisorSteam.png?t=1736177795\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2155320/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736177795","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2155320/page.bg.jpg?t=1736177795","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2155320/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1736177795","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2155320/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1736177795","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Partial Controller Support","id":18}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[2,5],"notes":"The final content may feature blood and violence, and sexual themes."},"detailed_description":"<h1